This task entails in making a Task Manager application that allows users to manage their daily tasks using a linked list.
Program will be able:
    1. Add tasks
        a. At the beginning (highest priority)
        b. At the end (lowest priority)
        c. At a specific position (custom priority)
    2. Delete tasks
        a. The first task (highest priority task)
        b. The last task (lowest priority task)
        c. A task at a specific position
    3. View tasks
        a. Display all tasks in order of their priority
    4. Search for a task
        a. Search for a task by its description and display its priority